Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉寒空中有自己所不熟悉的哀鸣在回响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:52.96,JM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(525,390)}{\fad(1500,0)}{\3c&H00CEA88C&}锈\N鸣\N声
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这镇上的病到底是从什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.32,0:03:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是十四年前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家表面看上去没什么不同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.01,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是皮肤各处都僵硬得可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手脚无法自由活动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最严重的是我的旧识
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连起床都…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个患者在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是单独住在西边的夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇子里的人都说 他们的女儿是病因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.27,0:03:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姑娘叫繁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从她出生后 周围的人就一个接一个地生病
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这的确是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但十四年间用尽了各种办法也找不到原因
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那姑娘也闭口不言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都只是怀疑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你 这月的份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么跟她父母是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有余力同情这种孩子还不如多给我们点报酬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 穿了个洞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 没备用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没完没了 这镇里的人可真不嫌烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是说句话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那传言是假的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是真的 也不是自己期望家人和朋友生病的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的村子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为两年前的风暴失去了半数的家人和朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就决定代替父亲一直在这里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.51,0:05:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也决定只能这么做 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问那姑娘的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是老爷请来的医生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什么也不知道 她一句话都不说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.35,0:05:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻 你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…繁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看见这锈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫银古
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被人叫来治病的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会说你什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想和你说说怎么治好这病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 即使出声也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想生锈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 没什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你也能看到锈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音是很可怕的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我感到会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与娇小的身体不符合的嘶哑声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那洞里 我一直叫到声音变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却有甜美生涩的残响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无论怎么改变声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的声音还是会诱使锈涌出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有不可思议回响的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.03,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爹 你回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那娃娃怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊 是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.32,0:08:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一出声 周围的人和物就会生锈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为那是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 繁 唱首歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱我喜欢的歌给大家听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 大家看不到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识到那是不好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我到了四岁 大家开始感到身体活动不自如的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.12,0:08:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那事和爹娘说了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁 这绝不能和任何人说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是说了就不能在这里呆下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经…不能干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在能活下去 都是靠那宅子里老爷的同情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在这里依赖同情欺骗大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到能够偿还的那一天为止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不要出声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那以后就没跟任何人讲过话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有十年没和人说过话了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大家憎恶也是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我选择了让全家三口活下来的这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.39,0:09:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.68,0:09:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这声音越听越奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能发出这种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是混杂着人所无法发出的层面的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你自己听来有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实你身边就有和你的声音极其相似的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是锈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫“野锈”的虫的活物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能看到的人 也有看不到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是与我们生存方式不同的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野锈一般是附着在生物尸体上将其分解的无害物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候就会发出声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音就像将这声音放大了数百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此山里的野锈就判断这里有吃的而集中过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却没食物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就连活着的东西都附上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是这样的话 让它们散开就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.06,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有取回你声音的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都附着 没有什么喜好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体都平均地染着锈色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这么冷的地方干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你不怕繁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到这镇子来才两年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是没有繁是病因的实感罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.62,0:12:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个野锈都没附上是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到海吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 大家的病痊愈 我也能出声的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能感谢彻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 虽说是除虫但要利用你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:13:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后想要安全生活 就必须离开这镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 病能治好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我什么都做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.04,0:13:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一件事要拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你教我写字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 手巾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.67,0:13:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 知道原因了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 繁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那只是谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.03,0:13:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我看看 读给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.01,0:13:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果和你说话你也会生病…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止都对不起了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻 这是谁写的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.81,0:14:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 还我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你也同情繁是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个给老爷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么 彻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追了 快从炉子里拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.65,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不会让她用“不知道”蒙混过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到别处去吧 繁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会被怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生还没教我除虫的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在姑且先从这里逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那山岭等着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会说服大家 然后到那里告诉你除虫的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也已经不能呆在这镇子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那山岭和我的村子在一个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人太危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.81,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做到吧 繁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银古先生 为什么包庇繁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出繁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使赶走繁也治不好病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是繁的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁只是和普通的孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话 笑 唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是那“声音”里有促使病因聚集的要素而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我们没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是她该怎么向生病的人们道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.63,0:16:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道歉的话 十年来繁一直在做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要打破禁忌 推脱个三言两语
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会增加大家的怀疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是罪的话 她一直背负至今
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不能就这样原谅她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的孩子跟那孩子同龄却不能走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 她会补偿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.18,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果呼唤那病的是繁的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能铲除的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你们不会算下帐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这病扯上关系的人都一样痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁 那信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总觉得字里行间你有要离开镇子的念头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病治好后你打算那么办吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目标吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.96,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 你也到我的村子里来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.43,0:17:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个不管房子还是船都基本被冲走的渔村
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.59,0:17:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家正在慢慢重建
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.67,0:17:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总能有办法的 就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.22,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来 出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须得求助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.38,0:18:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离这么远叫的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这病能治好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁 彻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会听错的那个声音 在山间回响
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.23,0:19:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像腿变轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗 彻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连彻都生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.73,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是丧失了意识而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 这小子没生病
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.72,0:19:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 我的腿…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果那时你做了近似我想让你做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,围绕这镇子的群山使声音回响
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聚集在镇里的野锈都四散到山里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.95,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 能做到这点的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有背对海的那个山岭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为野锈讨厌“潮气”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.40,0:20:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在能刮进海风的村子尽头附上的锈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是野锈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.38,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普通的锈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻没生病是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在渔村长大 来这里以后也不时吹吹海风的缘故吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.31,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 到海边去的话 就能正常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.13,0:20:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 散去的虫只是很小的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这以后不重复多年就无法全部除去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.82,0:21:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能真的还没除完你的声音就先完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有一点记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有充满锈的镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的我 非常喜欢这个镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一点也好 如果能回到那时的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑娘离开镇子 病就慢慢开始消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.53,0:21:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去山岭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.25,0:21:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在据说镇里的人能听见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎会穿破耳膜但异常美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛听过的歌声在山间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐约回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝野行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.80,0:00:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

